description:
The Count Basie Orchestra delivers a swinging rendition of "Back to The Apple" in Sweden, 1962.

Soloists: Frank Foster (tenor saxophone) and Al Aarons (trumpet).
Frank Foster is also the composer and arranger.

The rhythm section of this band is a powerhouse: Count Basie (piano), Eddie Jones (bass), Freddie Green (guitar) and Sonny Payne (drums).
